<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA71">
<l>iṭappāla vāṉat teḻumatiyai nīyōr</l>
<l>maṭappāvai taṉṉarukē vaittā - liṭap pākaṅ</l>
<l>koṇṭāṇ malaippāvai kūṟoṉṟuṅ kaṇṭilaṅkāṇ</l>
<l>kaṇṭāyē mukkaṇṇāy kaṇ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you place the moon rising in the sky on the left side</l>
<l>close to the unique youthful girl, we won’t see any part</l>
<l>of the mountain girl who has taken [your] left side, see.</l>
<l>Have you seen [her] by eye, three-eyed one?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
